906 __IO uint32_t RX_PAYSZ;
907 __IO uint32_t RXDR;
908 __IO uint32_t RX_ORDEXT1;
909 __IO uint32_t RX_ORDEXT2;
910} UCPD_TypeDef;

1222/******************** Bit definition for ADC_ISR register *******************/
1223#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Pos (0U)

1227#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Pos)

1230#define ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOC_Pos)
1231#define ADC_ISR_EOC ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk
1232#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos (3U)
1233#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos)
1234#define ADC_ISR_EOS ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk
1235#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos (4U)
1236#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos)
1237#define ADC_ISR_OVR ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk
1238#define ADC_ISR_JEOC_Pos (5U)
1239#define ADC_ISR_JEOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_JEOC_Pos)
1240#define ADC_ISR_JEOC ADC_ISR_JEOC_Msk
1241#define ADC_ISR_JEOS_Pos (6U)
1242#define ADC_ISR_JEOS_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_JEOS_Pos)
1243#define ADC_ISR_JEOS ADC_ISR_JEOS_Msk
1244#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos (7U)
1245#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos)

1294#define ADC_CR_ADEN_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_ADEN_Pos)
1295#define ADC_CR_ADEN ADC_CR_ADEN_Msk
1296#define ADC_CR_ADDIS_Pos (1U)
1297#define ADC_CR_ADDIS_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_ADDIS_Pos)
1298#define ADC_CR_ADDIS ADC_CR_ADDIS_Msk
1299#define ADC_CR_ADSTART_Pos (2U)
1300#define ADC_CR_ADSTART_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_ADSTART_Pos)
1301#define ADC_CR_ADSTART ADC_CR_ADSTART_Msk
1302#define ADC_CR_JADSTART_Pos (3U)
1303#define ADC_CR_JADSTART_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_JADSTART_Pos)
1304#define ADC_CR_JADSTART ADC_CR_JADSTART_Msk
1305#define ADC_CR_ADSTP_Pos (4U)
1306#define ADC_CR_ADSTP_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_ADSTP_Pos)
1307#define ADC_CR_ADSTP ADC_CR_ADSTP_Msk
1308#define ADC_CR_JADSTP_Pos (5U)
1309#define ADC_CR_JADSTP_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_JADSTP_Pos)
1310#define ADC_CR_JADSTP ADC_CR_JADSTP_Msk
1311#define ADC_CR_ADVREGEN_Pos (28U)
1312#define ADC_CR_ADVREGEN_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_ADVREGEN_Pos)
1313#define ADC_CR_ADVREGEN ADC_CR_ADVREGEN_Msk
1314#define ADC_CR_DEEPPWD_Pos (29U)
1315#define ADC_CR_DEEPPWD_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR_DEEPPWD_Pos)
1316#define ADC_CR_DEEPPWD ADC_CR_DEEPPWD_Msk
1317#define ADC_CR_ADCALDIF_Pos (30U)

11501/******************************************************************************/
11502/* */
11503/* USB Device FS Endpoint registers */
11504/* */
11505/******************************************************************************/
11506#define USB_EP0R USB_BASE
11507#define USB_EP1R (USB_BASE + 0x0x00000004)
11508#define USB_EP2R (USB_BASE + 0x0x00000008)
11509#define USB_EP3R (USB_BASE + 0x0x0000000C)
11510#define USB_EP4R (USB_BASE + 0x0x00000010)
11511#define USB_EP5R (USB_BASE + 0x0x00000014)
11512#define USB_EP6R (USB_BASE + 0x0x00000018)
11513#define USB_EP7R (USB_BASE + 0x0x0000001C)
11514
11515/* bit positions */
11516#define USB_EP_CTR_RX ((uint16_t)0x8000U)
11517#define USB_EP_DTOG_RX ((uint16_t)0x4000U)
11518#define USB_EPRX_STAT ((uint16_t)0x3000U)
11519#define USB_EP_SETUP ((uint16_t)0x0800U)
11520#define USB_EP_T_FIELD ((uint16_t)0x0600U)
11521#define USB_EP_KIND ((uint16_t)0x0100U)
11522#define USB_EP_CTR_TX ((uint16_t)0x0080U)
11523#define USB_EP_DTOG_TX ((uint16_t)0x0040U)
11524#define USB_EPTX_STAT ((uint16_t)0x0030U)
11525#define USB_EPADDR_FIELD ((uint16_t)0x000FU)
11526
11527/* EndPoint REGister MASK (no toggle fields) */
11528#define USB_EPREG_MASK (USB_EP_CTR_RX|USB_EP_SETUP|USB_EP_T_FIELD|USB_EP_KIND|USB_EP_CTR_TX|USB_EPADDR_FIELD)
11530#define USB_EP_TYPE_MASK ((uint16_t)0x0600U)
11531#define USB_EP_BULK ((uint16_t)0x0000U)
11532#define USB_EP_CONTROL ((uint16_t)0x0200U)
11533#define USB_EP_ISOCHRONOUS ((uint16_t)0x0400U)
11534#define USB_EP_INTERRUPT ((uint16_t)0x0600U)
11535#define USB_EP_T_MASK ((uint16_t) ~USB_EP_T_FIELD & USB_EPREG_MASK)
11536
11537#define USB_EPKIND_MASK ((uint16_t)~USB_EP_KIND & USB_EPREG_MASK)
11539#define USB_EP_TX_DIS ((uint16_t)0x0000U)
11540#define USB_EP_TX_STALL ((uint16_t)0x0010U)
11541#define USB_EP_TX_NAK ((uint16_t)0x0020U)
11542#define USB_EP_TX_VALID ((uint16_t)0x0030U)
11543#define USB_EPTX_DTOG1 ((uint16_t)0x0010U)
11544#define USB_EPTX_DTOG2 ((uint16_t)0x0020U)
11545#define USB_EPTX_DTOGMASK (USB_EPTX_STAT|USB_EPREG_MASK)
11547#define USB_EP_RX_DIS ((uint16_t)0x0000U)
11548#define USB_EP_RX_STALL ((uint16_t)0x1000U)
11549#define USB_EP_RX_NAK ((uint16_t)0x2000U)
11550#define USB_EP_RX_VALID ((uint16_t)0x3000U)
11551#define USB_EPRX_DTOG1 ((uint16_t)0x1000U)
11552#define USB_EPRX_DTOG2 ((uint16_t)0x2000U)
11553#define USB_EPRX_DTOGMASK (USB_EPRX_STAT|USB_EPREG_MASK)

13107/******************************************************************************/
13108/* For a painless codes migration between the STM32G4xx device product */
13109/* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
13110/* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
13111/* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
13112/* product lines within the same STM32G4 Family */
13113/******************************************************************************/
13114
13115/* Aliases for __IRQn */
13116#define TIM7_DAC_IRQn TIM7_IRQn
13117#define COMP4_5_6_IRQn COMP4_IRQn
13118
13119/* Aliases for __IRQHandler */
13120#define TIM7_DAC_IRQHandler TIM7_IRQHandler
13121#define COMP4_5_6_IRQHandler COMP4_IRQHandler
13122
13123#ifdef __cplusplus
13124}
13125#endif /* __cplusplus */
13126
13127#endif /* __STM32G431xx_H */
